{
  "_comment_target": "FSDP smoke test for the EgoWM-style legacy variant — same as train_drrobot_1k_10vids_egowm.json but without single_process so we exercise train_fsdp.py before committing to the full L40 run. 2 epochs × 10 videos × 8 GPUs ≈ 5 min wall-clock. Designed to catch any FSDP-specific bug in the egowm code path (e.g. unguarded render_fuse refs in train_fsdp.py).",

  "model_path": "Wan-AI/Wan2.1-I2V-14B-480P-Diffusers",
